{"tid":861440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開辦電競文憑育人才 英皇張焯然：電競選手非垃圾","createTime":"2018-10-14T06:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T07:02:26.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"150fa7f58cd135f43748a1ef71b7282d16eace69","tid":861440,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:42:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/張焯然-電競選手非垃圾-220413469.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fcelebrity%2F%E5%BC%B5%E7%84%AF%E7%84%B6-%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E9%9D%9E%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE-220413469.html&d=m6G9QNRFau2K256fxrbYNMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6df716e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/張焯然-電競選手非垃圾-220413469.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】英皇電競業務總監張焯然，昨日出席「共融電子競技隊邀請賽2018」，他表示電競運動不應分有沒有身體缺陷，雖然傷健人士和職業戰隊在訓練上會有分別，但希望能將電競運動作多層面的推廣。<br />\n<br />\n英皇電競積極推動本港電競行業發展，早前就和香港大學專業進修學院合作，開辦首個政府認可的「電子競技科學文憑」課程，張焯然指課程不是教人打機，而是講解整個行業的運作，藉此讓家長了解職業電競選手和打機的分別。他又謂今屆亞運首次加入電競比賽，雖然只列作示範項目，但金牌由香港人奪得，笑言電競選手不是垃圾。張焯然表示：「我們都想將電競正統化，正積極和政府溝通，希望日後能舉行學界電競比賽，雖然坊間有不少阻力，但我們會繼續努力。」"},{"pid":"2df305f7e17e695765364f3b54accda070ad670c","tid":861440,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"人地贏左奧運金牌先夠膽咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047e31a4ae3c08e2fb9d6b7830a8e0b0bc89305c","tid":861440,"uid":115441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"語言偽術將成件事美化到好美好<br />\n最攞命係個死人政府肯比$埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8d6df93d1eb8e22ebed2abef0bd562d40e9815","tid":861440,"uid":31330,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"我寧願d 錢拎去搞電競都唔撚想要個人工島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee6b300630013b36afef4a5efaf3db2c7c3afee","tid":861440,"uid":125213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:57:53.000Z","msg":"係臘鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7268eb27f7136558cc472cf342aa6fbd6f3c2b1","tid":861440,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:02:26.000Z","msg":"幾時過黎隻抽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}